  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->[discoveryMethod] the location of an infamous company of mercenaries. These ancient soldiers are from a long-forgotten era in the planet's history. They have recently awoken from cryptosleep and are causing trouble in the area.\n\nThe company is led by [LEADER_nameDef], who possesses a unique [WEAPON_quality] weapon. The group contains:\n\n[mercenaryList]\n\nIf you're able to capture or kill the leader, you can take the unique weapon.\n\n[location]</li>
